name: 5 STAR FISHY!!! Beta
description:
PINK FISHY WANTS REVENGE! ALL OF THE YEARS OF HUMANS AND HUMANS, HUMAN HUMAN HUMAN MAKES PINK FISHY VEEEEERRRRRY ANGRY!

Controls:

Space to play

R to restart

Mouse Cursor to control pink fishy

The game idea is inspired by Jonas Tyroller.  Also, this game is in an early state, and will likely recive updates, so stay tuned!
